    public class MaterialCountUp
extends gwt.material.design.client.base.AbstractValueWidget<Double>
    Animates a numerical value by counting it up with delightful animations.

    XML Namespace Declaration

     
 xmlns:ma='urn:import:gwt.material.design.addins.client'

    UiBinder Usage:

     
 <ma:countup.MaterialCountUp ui:field="lblNumber" startValue="0" endValue="100" />

    Java Usage:

     
 // To start the animation
 lblNumber.start();

    Author:
    kevzlou7979
    See Also:
    Material CountUp, CountUpJs 1.9.0
